protected void UploadButton_Click(object sender, EventArgs e)\n{\n    try\n    {\n        if (FileUploadControl.HasFile)\n        {\n            int fileSize = FileUploadControl.PostedFile.ContentLength;\n            if (fileSize > 1048576) // 1MB in bytes\n            {\n                LabelError.Text = "The file must be less than 1 MB!";\n                return; // do not proceed further\n            }\n\n            string fileName = Path.GetFileName(FileUploadControl.FileName);\n            FileUploadControl.SaveAs(Server.MapPath("~/uploads/") + fileName);\n\n            LabelStatus.Text = "File has been uploaded successfully.";\n        }\n    }\n    catch (Exception ex)\n    {\n        LabelError.Text = "An error occurred while uploading the file: " + ex.Message;\n    }\n}